    "description": "EazyDiner Ventures Solutions is actively seeking a talented and motivated Front Office Manager to join our dynamic team in Bhopal. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout EazyDiner Ventures Solutions:\nEazyDiner Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with EazyDiner Ventures Solutions!",
